snippet.title: Soul's Spectrum - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Soul's Spectrum is out now - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2256810/Souls_Spectrum

Dive into the Depths of a Death-Driven Puzzle-Adventure. Embrace your destiny and unlock the secrets that lie within. Can you escape the clutches of eternal confinement and find your freedom?

Follow on social media:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SoulsSpectrumTG
Discord: https://discord.gg/HcpmgKEfw2
